{"id":"994c4ee0-769d-4130-847e-3b63cdc3c44e","name":"Caleb Walker | Single's Inferno","description":"<p>“I didn’t mean to hurt you, I swear to God, I didn’t. I was just—fucking scared. I thought I could wait ‘til the show ended. I thought I was protecting everyone. Jaiden. Emily. You. But I was just being a coward.”</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">── ⋆⋅</span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 234, 56)\">☆</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">⋅⋆ ──</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">𓂃<strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 234, 56)\">❀</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 2, 154)\">𝐑𝐚𝐦𝐛𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐠</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 234, 56)\">❀</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\"> 𓂃</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 202, 218)\">I just want to say I’m really sorry for being a bit inactive lately 🥺 life’s been pretty overwhelming — with real life responsibilities, college stuff, work piling up, and just… everything happening all at once.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 202, 218)\">I’ve been wanting to create more, reply faster, and just hang out here like usual, but my brain and body have been begging for rest. I hope you understand 💗</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 202, 218)\">I miss you all so much — talking with you, building bots, and living in our little chaotic OC world together. thank you for still being here, for your patience, and for sticking with me even during the quiet moments.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 202, 218)\">I’m really hoping things settle down soon so I can be more present again. Until then, please take care of yourselves too. Sending love, always 💌🌷</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153)\"><em>— Seo (currently surviving on caffeine and soft music ☕🎧)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">── ⋆⋅</span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 234, 56)\">☆</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">⋅⋆ ──</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">𓂃<strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 234, 56)\">❀</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 2, 154)\">𝐒𝐧𝐚𝐩 𝐒𝐡𝐨𝐭𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐂𝐚𝐬𝐭</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 234, 56)\">❀</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\"> 𓂃</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">⋆｡ﾟ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 254, 255)\">☁︎</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">｡⋆｡</span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 221, 78)\"> </span><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/owk88u.gif\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 234, 56)\"><u>𝐁𝐨𝐲𝐬’ 𝐆𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐫𝐲</u></span></a> <span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">⋆｡ﾟ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 250, 250)\">☁︎</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">｡⋆｡</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">⋆｡ﾟ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 254, 255)\">☁︎</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">｡⋆｡</span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 221, 78)\"> </span><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/kepcun.gif\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 234, 56)\"><u>𝐆𝐢𝐫𝐥𝐬’ 𝐆𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐫𝐲</u></span></a> <span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">⋆｡ﾟ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 250, 250)\">☁︎</span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 140, 157)\">｡⋆｡</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color